# Research Worker Rules

- Separate Express server on :3001. Cannot import from src/lib/.
- Schemas/types must exist in BOTH the worker and the Next.js app.
- Each runner: primary phase -> repair phase -> rescue phase with fallback models.
- All runners use Anthropic SDK streaming with native web_search + tool loop.
- Results written to Supabase journey_sessions.research_results[section].
- Worker validates activeJourneyRunId before writing (prevents stale overwrites).
- Deploy separately: cd research-worker && railway up
